{"tid":1279063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［爆料］7月1日 你地既魯莽，已經變危險，警察入，有source俾你","createTime":"2019-07-02T14:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T14:49:58.000Z","uid":70888,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7a669c16a62b8a30e5d70599d2da775f41c000c0","tid":1279063,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"「魯莽駕駛」和「魯莽駕駛引致他人死亡」已自 2000 年 7 月 1 日起被「危險駕駛」和「危險駕駛引致他人死亡」所取代。另外，由 2010 年 12 月17 日開始，新增『危險駕駛引致他人身體受嚴重傷害』罪行條文，和再次加重危險駕駛罪行(包括「危險駕駛」和「危險駕駛引致他人死亡」）的刑罰，藉以提高阻嚇作用。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/safe_motoring_guides/dangerous_driving/index_t.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Froad_safety%2Fsafe_motoring_guides%2Fdangerous_driving%2Findex_t.html&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=da6095cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/safe_motoring_guides/dangerous_driving/index_t.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">食屎啦 屌你老母死警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比左料你喇，快d set roadblock 拉人啦，好撚危險呀，屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毅進仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />棄卒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma